00:19:26.120 --> 00:19:29.560
(Shanlifang Hotel Group Charity Gala Benefiting the Nature Foundation)

00:19:33.761 --> 00:19:35.321
Looks like Fei isn't here yet.

00:19:37.444 --> 00:19:38.880
