00:32:37.440 --> 00:32:38.440
So far,

00:32:38.521 --> 00:32:39.720
Shanlifang Hotel Group

00:32:39.840 --> 00:32:41.666
Has adopted world-class fresh air systems

00:32:41.733 --> 00:32:43.920
